{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/smart-home/cbi-isolator-esp-conversion","result":{"data":{"post":{"html":"<p>Some on their smart home journey, may have arrived at the time where they want to manage high loads remotely, such as a geyser. Typically, at least in South Africa, geysers come standard with a 3kW element which uses 13 amps. However in my own home, the geyser for the main bedroom was equipped with a 4kW element, which meant a whopping 18 amps! Most smart switches are rated 16 amp for the power metering switches or 10 amp for the non-metering options.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cbi-lowvoltage.co.za/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CBI-electric (Circuit Breaker Industries)</a> released a a few ‚Äúsmart‚Äù switches that can handle 30 amp. The one I have here is the <a href=\"https://cbi-lowvoltage.co.za/asi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CBI Astute Smart Isolator</a> or ASI for short.</p>\n<p>These are all built into the Tuya Smart IoT framework, which I am not a fan off. I prefer where possible using open-source software, including on the IoT devices in my house. In this guide, I will go over the process of converting one to just that!</p>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start.</p>\n<h3>üî© Components</h3>\n<p>You will need the following components:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cbi-lowvoltage.co.za/asi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CBI Astute Smart Isolator</a></li>\n<li>ESP-12S module from <a href=\"https://za.rs-online.com/web/p/wi-fi-modules/1697593\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">RS-Components</a> or <a href=\"https://www.banggood.com/5pcs-ESP8266-ESP-12S-Serial-WIFI-Wireless-Module-Transceiver-ESP8266-4M-Flash-p-1493538.html?p=DX050122090268201806&#x26;custlinkid=2697172\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Banggood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.banggood.com/ESP8266-Test-Board-Burner-Development-Board-WIFI-Module-For-ESP-01-ESP-01S-ESP-12E-ESP-12F-ESP-12S-ESP-18T-p-1684992.htmlp=DX050122090268201806&#x26;custlinkid=2697172\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ESP8266 development board</a> or any usb to serial adapter, such as the popular <a href=\"https://www.robotics.org.za/index.php?route=product/product&#x26;product_id=2499\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CH340G USB-Serial Converter</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can use the ESP-12F as well, but then you will require 2x 10k resistor in addition to the ESP-12F. The recommendation is a 10k 0805 SMD resistor and a 10k 1/4w leaded resistor.</p>\n<h3>üî© Flashing Tasmota to the ESP-12S</h3>\n<p>First up, let‚Äôs program our new controller. I am using my <a href=\"https://www.banggood.com/ESP8266-Test-Board-Burner-Development-Board-WIFI-Module-For-ESP-01-ESP-01S-ESP-12E-ESP-12F-ESP-12S-ESP-18T-p-1684992.htmlp=DX050122090268201806&#x26;custlinkid=2697172\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ESP8266 development board</a> here. This makes the process convenient and easy.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(1.7730496453900708* 80vh), 1000px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/eacc7/esp-12s-programming.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/70216/esp-12s-programming.webp 250w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/61bdd/esp-12s-programming.webp 500w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/d0dac/esp-12s-programming.webp 1000w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/7d819/esp-12s-programming.webp 1100w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/b6501/esp-12s-programming.jpg 250w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/bb312/esp-12s-programming.jpg 500w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/4edc6/esp-12s-programming.jpg 1000w,\n/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/eacc7/esp-12s-programming.jpg 1100w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/69d6f28ee7260571582079f0852194b6/4edc6/esp-12s-programming.jpg\"\n            alt=\"ESP Programmer\"\n            title=\"ESP Programmer\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Using the <a href=\"https://www.robotics.org.za/index.php?route=product/product&#x26;product_id=2499\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">esptool</a> from Github, this is the command I used after downloading the Tasmota firmware binary.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">esptool.py <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--port</span> /dev/cu.usbserial-A9UD533R write_flash 0x00000 Downloads/tasmota.bin</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Taking the CBI ASI apart</h3>\n<p>Brand new ASI removed from packaging:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(0.7507507507507507* 80vh), 750.8px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/e35d9/cbi-isolator-01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.20000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/70216/cbi-isolator-01.webp 250w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/61bdd/cbi-isolator-01.webp 500w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/d0dac/cbi-isolator-01.webp 1000w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/21231/cbi-isolator-01.webp 1500w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/521a5/cbi-isolator-01.webp 2000w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/84cd4/cbi-isolator-01.webp 3000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/b6501/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 250w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/bb312/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 500w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/4edc6/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/92dea/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 1500w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 2000w,\n/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/e35d9/cbi-isolator-01.jpg 3000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d9ee49ef4e9370100df8d3813f9e3ffa/4edc6/cbi-isolator-01.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 01\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 01\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(0.7507507507507507* 80vh), 750.8px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/e35d9/cbi-isolator-02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.20000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/70216/cbi-isolator-02.webp 250w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/61bdd/cbi-isolator-02.webp 500w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/d0dac/cbi-isolator-02.webp 1000w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/21231/cbi-isolator-02.webp 1500w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/521a5/cbi-isolator-02.webp 2000w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/84cd4/cbi-isolator-02.webp 3000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/b6501/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 250w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/bb312/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 500w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/4edc6/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 1000w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/92dea/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 1500w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 2000w,\n/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/e35d9/cbi-isolator-02.jpg 3000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/75f1dafc964fb532f8e4d3574e88a38a/4edc6/cbi-isolator-02.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 02\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 02\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>First cover removed and we can see the 30A relay:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(0.7507507507507507* 80vh), 750.8px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/e35d9/cbi-isolator-03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.20000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/70216/cbi-isolator-03.webp 250w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/61bdd/cbi-isolator-03.webp 500w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/d0dac/cbi-isolator-03.webp 1000w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/21231/cbi-isolator-03.webp 1500w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/521a5/cbi-isolator-03.webp 2000w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/84cd4/cbi-isolator-03.webp 3000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/b6501/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 250w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/bb312/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 500w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/4edc6/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/92dea/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 1500w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 2000w,\n/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/e35d9/cbi-isolator-03.jpg 3000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d934f2853145bc0b9724d16c38010b66/4edc6/cbi-isolator-03.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 03\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 03\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Further removal will reveal the WR3E micro controller:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(1.3297872340425532* 80vh), 1000px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/b28f0/cbi-isolator-04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/70216/cbi-isolator-04.webp 250w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/61bdd/cbi-isolator-04.webp 500w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/d0dac/cbi-isolator-04.webp 1000w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/21231/cbi-isolator-04.webp 1500w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/521a5/cbi-isolator-04.webp 2000w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/b7fd3/cbi-isolator-04.webp 4000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/b6501/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 250w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/bb312/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 500w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/4edc6/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 1000w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/92dea/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 1500w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 2000w,\n/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/b28f0/cbi-isolator-04.jpg 4000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/560fb8a18cc29a58ededc127028087a2/4edc6/cbi-isolator-04.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 04\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 04\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Desoldering</h3>\n<p>I start by putting the board into something to hold it well in place while I work with heat.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(1.3297872340425532* 80vh), 1000px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/b28f0/cbi-isolator-05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/70216/cbi-isolator-05.webp 250w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/61bdd/cbi-isolator-05.webp 500w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/d0dac/cbi-isolator-05.webp 1000w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/21231/cbi-isolator-05.webp 1500w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/521a5/cbi-isolator-05.webp 2000w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/b7fd3/cbi-isolator-05.webp 4000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/b6501/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 250w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/bb312/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 500w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/4edc6/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 1000w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/92dea/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 1500w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 2000w,\n/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/b28f0/cbi-isolator-05.jpg 4000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/33780aa000b6cd4c753dadb709ab3af3/4edc6/cbi-isolator-05.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 05\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 05\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>My eye sight is also not what it used to be for something up close so I need some help.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(1.3297872340425532* 80vh), 1000px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/b28f0/cbi-isolator-06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/70216/cbi-isolator-06.webp 250w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/61bdd/cbi-isolator-06.webp 500w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/d0dac/cbi-isolator-06.webp 1000w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/21231/cbi-isolator-06.webp 1500w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/521a5/cbi-isolator-06.webp 2000w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/b7fd3/cbi-isolator-06.webp 4000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/b6501/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 250w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/bb312/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 500w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/4edc6/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 1000w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/92dea/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 1500w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/cbe2c/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 2000w,\n/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/b28f0/cbi-isolator-06.jpg 4000w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/97540fcfcacc44a2d8ddf6cc5a1c51db/4edc6/cbi-isolator-06.jpg\"\n            alt=\"cbi isolator 06\"\n            title=\"cbi isolator 06\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Once the WR3E is removed, this is what it looks like.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; max-width: clamp(200px, calc(1.3297872340425532* 80vh), 1000px); max-height: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/b28f0/cbi-isolator-07.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/70216/cbi-isolator-07.webp 250w,\n/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/61bdd/cbi-isolator-07.webp 500w,\n/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/d0dac/cbi-isolator-07.webp 1000w,\n/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/21231/cbi-isolator-07.webp 1500w,\n/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/521a5/cbi-isolator-07.webp 2000w,\n/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/b7fd3/cbi-isolator-07.webp 4000w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e9e899f432094cf9423e9b09c66bf135/b6501/cbi-isolator-07.jpg 250w,\n/static/e9e899f432094